<p class="has-white-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-78b22f91fae1bcc933b4b69de92e7a4d"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="761" height="125" class="wp-image-7347" style="width: 752px" src="https://www.msd-salud-animal.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/sites/44/2025/10/logo-espanol.png" alt="" srcset="https://www.msd-salud-animal.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/sites/44/2025/10/logo-espanol.png 761w, https://www.msd-salud-animal.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/sites/44/2025/10/logo-espanol.png?resize=300,49 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 761px) 100vw, 761px" /></p>



<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-cryptium-pastel-blue-color has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" id="descubra-o"><strong>Tu ganado, siempre</strong><br><strong>bajo control</strong></h1>



<p class="has-white-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c194d051f99cb02e1f17c8c460f2580e" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)"><strong><mark class="has-inline-color has-cryptium-pastel-blue-color">SenseHub®</mark></strong> detecta cambios en salud, celo y comportamiento, para que tomes decisiones a tiempo.&nbsp;</p>



